Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Pre===================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 能现在就给我签个名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真宠女儿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有了女儿也会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得冈崎同学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很像爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 和这家伙像么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个月了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个月了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这问题真傻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很辛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有朋也君在 我很放心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止都两人一起努力过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.69,0:00:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像那时的秋生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间有了渚时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋生也说「由我来守护」的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧你这没本事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没本事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:00:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 已经不能继续这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.98,0:01:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚会辞掉工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我要独自撑起三个人的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 到了我们一家的紧要关头了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然想到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸在生我之前 是否也想过这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================OP===================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:42.97,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}熟悉的坡道上 却已不见你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:48.65,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}柔和的阳光 透过树叶投下斑点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.73,0:01:53.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}我独自一人 伫立在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:02:01.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}回顾着那些 温暖的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:09.31,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}只有你 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:15.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}在变幻的时间中 永驻我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:23.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}风吹而过 泪水渗眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:30.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}你的身影 已变得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.30,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}任何时候都不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.47,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}哪怕一切的一切全部改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:36.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}不忘记那一件 那一件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.06,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}稀松平常之事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.17,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}终会让你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:43.39,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}那被光芒包裹着的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}守护 守护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:48.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\be1}直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Text===================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有孩子了啊 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夫人生孩子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OH Congratulation Mr.冈崎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没出生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳野先生 你从哪得知的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我家夫人听早苗说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻里也都知道了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖的邻里消息网…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在社会上还没站稳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样一来不得不成为像样的丈夫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实说实话还没什么真实感…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等生出来了 你无论如何都会感受到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到任何人都无法独自生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都在成为着别人的支柱 又依偎着别人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.51,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在浩瀚的宇宙的一角 地球诞生后又过了45亿年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故而…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时光转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入第三个月时 孕吐加剧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚变得经常躺在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 要添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意 这点事情就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都要共同完成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太吃得下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么缓解的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说孕吐连机理都还不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只吃些稀流质 也会恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补充水分也要这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得下时就吃一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋也君做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不熟练 所以形状很那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 那我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不断变幻的时间中 我和渚不断努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能起床了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天状况非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生说过第十周左右会稳定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说一切顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想商量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在这屋子里把宝宝生下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这办得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在医院拿了这本未来妈妈教室的指南
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在家里生孩子的母亲写的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由父亲来给初生的婴儿洗第一次澡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在医院的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能无法马上抱到出生的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想 要是能马上抱到就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我和朋也君的家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在自己家 在这个小镇生下宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 家 里 生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的漂移怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能别玩游戏么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 光是生产已经很费事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还要选在自己家里生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然医生也担心渚的身体状况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想尽可能满足她的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也要考虑身体因素
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母子平安才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我生渚的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就和初生的渚分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋生也是在医护人员之后抱的渚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是我第一个舔她的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被做过那种事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太可爱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使可爱也不能那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你同意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要身体没问题就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你第一个去抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要由我来第一个舔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 舔也要由朋也君先来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不会舔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会舔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻傻的父女…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是八木小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的助产医师朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是八木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是冈崎渚 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是她丈夫朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说希望在这里生孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方也没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是可以放松的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间还很充裕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以慢慢考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事请随时联系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八木小姐也知道渚的身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说旁人的担心会让孕妇不安 要多加注意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才和妈妈说了些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…有点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用隐瞒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于我的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君和爸爸妈妈的担心我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使有什么万一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想把宝宝生下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家这么齐心协力 就是为了能平安生产啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想起高中时代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时为了表演的成功 也大家一起努力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想着和那时很像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗 我就是爸爸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能撒谎的 这孩子会信以为真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子的娃连玩笑都不懂么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是渚的孩子 所以开不了玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用那称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像秋生是想被叫成「阿秋」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿秋哦 阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别进行奇怪的胎教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长到这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有了可以听见外界声响的耳朵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找些音乐来听听也很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都唱歌给宝宝听的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子 团子 团子 团子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子大家族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子 团子 团子 团子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:11:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子大家族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子宝宝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可能在内心的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已预感到了那一刻的来临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点不舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天渚来了电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赶来一看 渚倒在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也该告诉我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我不想妨碍到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别担心 宝宝很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事尽管叫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天起 每天白天我都会陪在渚身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样朋也也能放心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不想要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朋也君在身边就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你是个很坚强的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别担心 朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我并没…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一起肯定能克服的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有朋也君守护着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经无法再完全沉浸在幸福感之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 早苗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚就是在这工作的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想来看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很新潮的店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这词已经不用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.27,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ナウい(新潮)=NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事要谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生说 分娩时可能会伴随危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只和我说了 还没有告诉渚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会…有多危险？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道会危及渚的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲所承受的负担会比平常的分娩更大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是生产本身大概不会有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只是一切顺利的情况下如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也也知道吧 渚常常会病倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚的病在很多方面是个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以医生也在担心是否会有万一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是必须慎重考虑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我先找朋也谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由朋也来告诉渚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后两人一起和医生商量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此基础上我也会一起想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想见到最糟的事态…就该放弃孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是越早越好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位好好想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗 谢谢您总为我们两个操心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想生下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你会这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很柔弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不想为此舍弃宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让宝宝平安 不在家里生也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见到宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说如果选择医院 能减少风险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 我还是担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚的想法不会改了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 她或许也非常不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上很开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但或许其实和我一样矛盾着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的秘密游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总在这里和小孩打打棒球 或是坐着发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作中经常不知所踪 原来是来这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:29.79,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:31.49,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿树被砍得越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这里很快会建大医院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.27,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续两年前的说的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在剧团演戏 早苗在教书时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也说过 那时的渚总是孤零零的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我和早苗留下发烧的渚去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都无论如何都脱不开身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚的病情已经稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我和早苗打算很快就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…渚等在了外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我们 直到倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天快亮时 已经几乎无可挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没体会过那种悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后的事 我以前只对早苗说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来时 我在抱着渚奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡乱跑着 不知何时就来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈求着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「救救渚吧 我不要这样的结局」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的 也只剩下祈求了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:18:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 这里的绿色似乎将渚包裹了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为那是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流着眼泪 感谢着万物的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后 就一直守望着这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里分明就是渚的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不可思议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事情真的就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望不可能是祈求了就能实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想尽办法 费尽心力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许能避开些最坏的结局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是建议要生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由最苦恼的人决定就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其结果有大家守望着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后你大概会遭遇痛苦与悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们…我们 一定能克服过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互支持着走下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风这么凉爽 真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才动了动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「哧溜」地动了动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要男孩女孩两种名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从朋也君名字里拿一个字来用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…还是由你的名字来想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将给予姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…「渚」很难直接套用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成「渚子」「渚美」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用直接套用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和「渚」相关的名字也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「汐」如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是海水涨落的潮「汐」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就男孩女孩都适用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎汐…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生会遭遇很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:04.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,410)}潮汐起落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些结果 在时光流转之中会回到自己身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这循环中 我会一直守望着汐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起「渚」来 「汐」更宏大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:14.11,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(345,410)}海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:14.11,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(465,410)}海潮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是大海呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成长为那种
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有包容一切 抚育一切的胸怀的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天也没能去海边啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也想和朋也君一起看看海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 做个约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年就和汐一起 三人去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能答应我吧 渚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================ED===================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:25.87,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}双眼凝视着 流动的云朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:32.79,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}心中感受着 天空变幻的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:40.98,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伫立不前的我们 察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:48.00,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}这变迁的世界编织出的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:55.24,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伸出的指尖 不断寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:23:03.93,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那恒久不变的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:11.49,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起的手中火炬闪亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:19.22,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那是通向明天的小小路标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:26.55,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}现在也在不断回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:34.08,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那一天的话语 终将化为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:38.84,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}推动我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Next===================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起的世界可能不止一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有学说认为 多种多样的世界平行存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤林 以前你谈起占卜时也说过这样的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是只有一个固定的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.95,0:24:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是有着各种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也这么想
